			"offsets": {
				"from": 0,
				"to": 3080
			},
			"text": " Hey, this is Brian from Fullstack Egg."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:03,080",
				"to": "00:00:04,920"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 3080,
				"to": 4920
			},
			"text": " When we set up paperless,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:04,920",
				"to": "00:00:07,560"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 4920,
				"to": 7560
			},
			"text": " we use something called Docker,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:07,560",
				"to": "00:00:10,360"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 7560,
				"to": 10360
			},
			"text": " and I'm going to tell you a little bit about it."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:10,360",
				"to": "00:00:16,520"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 10360,
				"to": 16520
			},
			"text": " You can think of Docker like a collection of shipping containers that all have different things inside,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:16,520",
				"to": "00:00:21,040"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 16520,
				"to": 21040
			},
			"text": " but because they are all inside of that same container,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:21,040",
				"to": "00:00:23,640"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 21040,
				"to": 23640
			},
			"text": " it makes it really easy to manage,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:23,640",
				"to": "00:00:27,080"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 23640,
				"to": 27080
			},
			"text": " and Docker does the same thing for software."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:27,080",
				"to": "00:00:31,480"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 27080,
				"to": 31480
			},
			"text": " Instead of installing a program and hoping it works on your computer,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:31,480",
				"to": "00:00:35,240"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 31480,
				"to": 35240
			},
			"text": " everything the program needs gets packed into a container."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:35,240",
				"to": "00:00:38,640"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 35240,
				"to": 38640
			},
			"text": " So when you run that container, it just works,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:38,640",
				"to": "00:00:42,520"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 38640,
				"to": 42520
			},
			"text": " and it doesn't matter if you're running it on your desktop computer"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:42,520",
				"to": "00:00:46,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 42520,
				"to": 46800
			},
			"text": " or on a VPS in the cloud, it always works the same."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:46,800",
				"to": "00:00:50,640"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 46800,
				"to": 50640
			},
			"text": " So this is Docker desktop on my Mac,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:50,640",
				"to": "00:00:55,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 50640,
				"to": 55000
			},
			"text": " and these are the containers running paperless right now on my computer."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:55,000",
				"to": "00:00:58,440"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 55000,
				"to": 58440
			},
			"text": " There's a few of them working together, one for the database,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:58,440",
				"to": "00:01:00,320"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 58440,
				"to": 60320
			},
			"text": " one for paperless itself,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:00,320",
				"to": "00:01:03,480"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 60320,
				"to": 63480
			},
			"text": " and one for the search add-on that we built."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:03,480",
				"to": "00:01:07,600"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 63480,
				"to": 67600
			},
			"text": " And here I'll show you them running in the terminal as well."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:07,600",
				"to": "00:01:10,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 67600,
				"to": 70000
			},
			"text": " Each one is running in its own little box,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:10,000",
				"to": "00:01:12,320"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 70000,
				"to": 72320
			},
			"text": " keeping things clean and separate."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:12,320",
				"to": "00:01:15,040"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 72320,
				"to": 75040
			},
			"text": " And while this all might seem complicated,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:15,040",
				"to": "00:01:18,080"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 75040,
				"to": 78080
			},
			"text": " you really don't have to be a programmer to set this up."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:18,080",
				"to": "00:01:21,000"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 78080,
				"to": 81000
			},
			"text": " Docker handles all the complicated parts."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:21,000",
				"to": "00:01:23,080"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 81000,
				"to": 83080
			},
			"text": " You basically say, \"Run this,\""
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:23,080",
				"to": "00:01:26,160"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 83080,
				"to": 86160
			},
			"text": " and it pulls everything down and starts it up."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:26,160",
				"to": "00:01:30,440"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 86160,
				"to": 90440
			},
			"text": " And if something breaks, you throw away the container and start fresh."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:30,440",
				"to": "00:01:34,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 90440,
				"to": 94400
			},
			"text": " Your data is stored separately, so nothing gets lost."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:34,400",
				"to": "00:01:36,760"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 94400,
				"to": 96760
			},
			"text": " So that's Docker in a nutshell."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:36,760",
				"to": "00:01:40,240"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 96760,
				"to": 100240
			},
			"text": " It packages software, so it runs the same everywhere,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:40,240",
				"to": "00:01:43,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 100240,
				"to": 103400
			},
			"text": " and you don't have to worry about installing all these dependencies"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:43,400",
				"to": "00:01:45,400"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 103400,
				"to": 105400
			},
			"text": " and breaking things."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:45,400",
				"to": "00:01:48,760"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 105400,
				"to": 108760
			},
			"text": " And for the paperless install videos,"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:48,760",
				"to": "00:01:52,760"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 108760,
				"to": 112760
			},
			"text": " you'll see that our setup script handles all the Docker stuff for you,"
